spell_list.description: Modifies the Necromancer's primary pets. The warlock pet's spells will become more difficult to be resisted, the warrior pet will take less damage and the scout pet gains increased combat skills and ability hit rates.
spell_list.description_pvp: Modifies the Necromancer's primary pets. The warlock pet's spells will become more difficult to be resisted, the warrior pet will take less damage and the scout pet gains increased combat skills and ability hit rates.

effect_list.description: Improves combat art hit chances by 6%, as well as the piercing and slashing skills of your scout pet.
Grants your fighter pet 4% damage absorption
Improves resistibility reduction of mage pet spells by 6%
